                    "bottom":{
                            "html":"<h3>Super Extreme DUI<\/h3><p>Penalties are even harsher for drivers charged with a BAC of .20 or more. Those charged will face a minimum of 45 days in jail without aggressive representation. License suspension, revocation of driving privileges, and long term interlock device requirements may become reality without a strong legal defense. Pinnacle Law will work hard to reduce your penalties or even possibly dismiss your case completely.<\/p>"
