                    "bottom":{
                            "html":"<h3>Aggravated DUI<\/h3><p>This felony charge has the power to cause permanent damage to your personal record and requires prison time of 4 months to 3.75 years. This type of DUI occurs under the following circumstances:<\/p><ul><li>&mdash; DUI while your license is suspended or revoked<\/li><li>&mdash; Two or more DUIs within 84 months<\/li><li>&mdash; DUI with a child under 15 years of age in the vehicle<\/li><li>&mdash; DUI while under ignition interlock device (IID) restriction<\/li><\/ul>"
                        }
